ReportDescr: Users are unable to log in using their Google account.
There is no option to export data from the analytics module.
It takes more than 10 seconds to load the main dashboard after login.
User's last login date is displayed as today's date instead of the actual last login.
Clicking on the "Help" link in the footer leads to a 404 error.
Error message doesn't display when mandatory fields are left blank during registration.
Elements on the dashboard are not aligned properly on smaller screens.
Fonts appear distorted in the user profile section.
The mobile app crashes immediately after launching on Android devices.
Users do not receive push notifications for new messages on the mobile app.
Sorting orders by date in ascending order sometimes shows incorrect sequence.
Graphs and charts do not render correctly in the analytics module.
Search functionality in the knowledge base takes too long to return results.
Sales figures for last quarter are showing as zero instead of the correct values.
Email notifications for upcoming events are sent at irregular intervals.
Password reset emails are not being delivered to users' inboxes.
Submitting a form with invalid data does not highlight the fields with errors.
The "Learn More" button on the pricing page directs to an empty page.
Clicking on the "Submit" button in the expense report section consistently crashes the desktop application.
Users cannot change their profile pictures after initial registration.
Notification badges on the app icon do not clear after checking notifications.
Editing and saving a document in the editor occasionally results in loss of formatting.
Scrolling on home page in mobile app causes pictures to disappear on iPhone.
Generating reports from the admin panel is significantly slow.
User's subscription level is incorrectly listed as "Basic" instead of "Premium".
Opening the settings menu causes the iOS app to freeze and crash.
Special characters in the input fields cause the form to fail submission without clear error messaging.
Scheduled email notifications feature is absent from the settings menu.
The Terms of Service link in the registration email is broken.
User permissions intermittently fail to update despite successful changes in the admin panel.
